<div id="parallax-world-of-ugg">
  <section>
    <div class="parallax-one">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="banner-index-content">
        <h1>Discover all the challenges</h1>
        <br>
        <h2>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and test yourself</h2>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="arrow-btn d-flex justify-content-center pt-5 mt-5">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg light-white-button" href="#chal-index" role="button"><i class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container container-scoring">
  <div class="container scoring-bloc bg-white pt-3">
    <h4 class="text-center mb-4 trophy">Top users <%= image_tag "trophy.png" %></h4>
  <table class="table">
    <%@best_five_users.each_with_index do |user, i| %>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <th scope="row">
          <% if [0, 1, 2].include?(i) %>
            <h5><%= image_tag "medaille#{i + 1}.png" %></h5>
          <% else %>
            <h5 class="number pl-2 avatar-padding"><%= i + 1 %></h5>
          <% end %>
        </th>
        <td><%= cl_image_tag user.avatar, class: "avatar" %></td>
        <td><%= user.username.capitalize %></td>
        <td><span id="score"><b><%= user.score %></b> points</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
    <% end %>
  </table>
  </div>

  <div class="scoring-infos mt-2">
    <h3 class="mb-5"><span class="highlight">Gain points</span> through your challenge !</h3>
    <h5>1. Daily survey</h5>
    <p>Once you've susbcrive to a challenge, everyday you'll see a "daily survey" in your Dashboard.
    They will be three questions and, depending on you daily habbits, you will obtain a certain amount of points.</p>
    <h5>2. Tips</h5>
    <p>Every challenge has several tips, helping you to improve yours habbits and consommation.
    You can pin them to your dashboard and once you have finished them, you will aslo gain points !</p>
    <h3>Begin now and take the lead !</h3>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page-prez ml-5 my-3">
  <div class="text-center mb-5 mt-5">
    <div class="challenge-list my-5">
      <h3>Challenge for <%= Date.today.strftime("%B") %>:
      <% @challenges.each do |challenge| %>
        <%= link_to challenge_path(challenge.id) do %>
          <span class="highlight"><%= challenge.title if challenge.date.strftime("%B") == Date.today.strftime("%B") %></span>
        <% end %>
      <% end %></h3>
    </div>
    <p>A new challenge is unlocked every month. You can subscribe to as many challenges as you like.</p>
    <p>Click on a card below to see more details about one challenge.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="options pb-4" id="chal-index">

  <% @challenges.each do |challenge| %>

    <% if challenge.date.strftime("%B") == Date.today.strftime("%B") %>

      <div class="option active" style="--optionBackground: linear-gradient(rgba(200, 200, 200, 0.5), rgba(0, 100, 100, 0.5)), url(<%= challenge.photo %>);">
        <%= link_to challenge_path(challenge.id) do %>
          <div class="label">
            <div class="icon"><img src="<%= challenge.badge %>" alt="badge"></div>
            <div class="info">
              <div class="main"><%= challenge.title %></div>
              <div class="sub"><%= challenge.date.strftime("%B") %></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

    <% else %>

      <div class="option" style="--optionBackground: linear-gradient(rgba(200, 200, 200, 0.5), rgba(0, 100, 100, 0.5)), url(<%= challenge.photo %>);">
        <%= link_to challenge_path(challenge.id) do %>
          <div class="label">
            <div class="icon"><img src="<%= challenge.badge %>" alt="badge"></div>
            <div class="info">
              <div class="main"><%= challenge.title %></div>
              <div class="sub"><%= challenge.date.strftime("%B") %></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

    <% end %>

  <% end %>

</div>
